FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_BOWL
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_BOWL

FCR21AU.original: ~z~That was quick, Niko. You would almost think you didn't want to sit down and converse with your cousin.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~太快了，Niko。感觉都来不及和自己的兄弟坐下来聊上几句。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~That is one funny man, Niko. Good choice.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~实在太好笑了，Niko。明智之选。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Niko, when will you learn? Your cousin is better than you at pool. You are no match.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~Niko，你什么时候才能明白？你堂兄比你更擅长台球，你太弱了。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Niko, that was fun. I was at a place belonging to Mikhail Faustin and I was not even shot.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~Niko，玩得很开心。我在Mikhail Faustin的地盘，还没有挨枪子儿。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~NB, the big man. Let's hustle.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~NB，大腕，赶紧走他。

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_DROPOFF
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_DROPOFF

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Get ready to watch a master at work. I am to darts what Perseus is to clothing.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~等着看大师级技术吧。我就是飞镖界的神之子服饰。

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_LEAVE_STRIP_GOOD
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_LEAVE_STRIP_GOOD

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_LEAVE_SHOW_CABARET
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_LEAVE_SHOW_CABARET

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_LEAVE_SHOW_COMEDY
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_LEAVE_SHOW_COMEDY

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVEF_LATE
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVEF_LATE

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Niko, I like to finish my darts games. Maybe next time we do that.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~Niko，我更想把这局飞镖投完。下次投完吧。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~That would have been even more fun if I hadn't been fearing for my life. Your Russian gangster friends are scary.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~要不是担心自己的人身安全，我会更享受一点的。你的俄国黑帮朋友太可怕了。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Niko, this is meant to be a very funny man. Anything you do not understand, you ask me and I will explain.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~Niko，他说的其实都很有趣。哪里没听懂尽管问，我会解释的。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~I did not expect an opportunity to kick your ass at darts. How could I refuse?
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~没想到还有机会在飞镖上把你干爆。我怎么会拒绝呢？

FCR21AU.original: ~z~We are the perfect match, cousin. A tie. That is unheard of, no?
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~我们是完美的对手，堂弟。平局了。闻所未闻不是吗？

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Niko, how could you want to leave so early. You haven't been hanging out at Hercules Nightclub or something have you?
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~Niko，怎么这么快就走了。你该不会是大力神夜店的常客吧？

FCR21AU.original: ~z~We have truly made it, Niko. The cousins Bellic eating in the finest dining rooms in Liberty City.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~我们真的成功了，Niko。Bellic兄弟在自由城最好的餐厅吃饭。

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_DIFF_DARTS_YES
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_DIFF_DARTS_YES

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_LEAVE_STRIP_OK
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_LEAVE_STRIP_OK

FCR21AU.original: ~z~American fast-food. Just think we could have the exact same meal in the Old Country.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~美式快餐。要是在故国也能吃到一样的饭菜就好了。

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVEF_NOTLATE_CAR
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVEF_NOTLATE_CAR

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Okay cousin, let's hit the alleys.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~好了堂弟，我们上球道吧。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Nothing hits the spot like a Burger Shot, cousin. My fifth chin is all thanks to these guys.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~吃得饱汉堡我喜欢吃，堂弟。我的五层下巴多亏了他们。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Niko, I don't like to stop things half way though. Ask any lady, I always satisfy.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~Niko，我不喜欢半途而废。找个女人问问，我总是能满足她们。

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_LATE
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_LATE

FCR21AU.original: ~z~My one and only cousin, except for the other ones. Let's go.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~我独一无二的堂弟，仅此一个。走吧。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~This is real entertainment, cousin. It's hard to find performances of this premium quality, even on Burlesque.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~这是真的好看，堂弟。这种质量的表演就算在Burlesque也是只此一家。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~I like that guy Niko. He sure is funny.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~我喜欢那个人，Niko。他真的很有趣。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Old Vlad's bar. We shall see if he can add our drinks to the rest of my debt.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~老Vlad开的酒吧。应该问他能不能把喝的酒记在我的账上。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~There you are cousin, let's move.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~你来啦，堂弟，我们走。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~I have been wanting to see this act, cousin. My friend saw this and he pissed in his pants.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~我一直都很想看这场演出，堂弟。我朋友看过，看得他笑尿了。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Those are the best burgers in Liberty City. I promise you this, cousin.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~那些是自由城最好的汉堡。我跟你保证，堂弟。

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_BOWL_LEAVE_WON
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_BOWL_LEAVE_WON

FCR21AU.original: ~z~It was a great restaurant but do not expect me to sleep with you now, cousin. I am not one of your girlfriends.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~餐馆很不错，不过别指望我跟你睡，堂弟。我不是你女朋友。

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_HIGHEND
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_HIGHEND

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Cousin, you know these things scare me. No matter, we go.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~堂弟，你也知道我怕这玩意的。算了，走吧。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~We're here Niko. Let's do some bowling.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~我们到了，Niko。进去打几球吧。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Finally cousin, you're late. We should go now.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~终于来了，堂弟，你迟到了。我们该走了。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~This is a good idea. It will remind us how lucky we are to have gotten out of the Old Country.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~这是个好主意，好让我们知道能离开故国有多幸运。

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_BOWL_LEAVE_DRAW
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_BOWL_LEAVE_DRAW

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Disgraceful to keep your cousin waiting. Well, we go now.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~让你堂兄等着可不是好事。算了，出发吧。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~I'm sorry for beating you cousin, but I'm the better player. That is it.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~很遗憾，我打赢你了，堂弟，我才是更强的选手。就是这样。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Faustin's Club, eh? So this is where he hangs out when he's not shooting innocent men in their stomachs.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~Faustin的俱乐部，嗯？这就是他没往无辜平民肚子上开洞时候待的地方吗。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Niko, good to see you, let's go.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~Niko，很高兴见到你，我们走吧。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Niko. Good to see you. We need to find a vehicle.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~Niko，很高兴见到你。我们得找辆车。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Niko, the phonebook on my cell is filling up so many hot chicks are giving me their numbers.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~Niko，我的通讯录里多得是主动给我电话的辣妹。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~My cousin, is so good to see you. Let's do this.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~我的堂弟，见到你真好。我们走吧。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Shit, I hope to God that Vlad isn't here.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~靠，我诚心诚意地希望Vlad不在这儿。

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_POOL_LEAVE_LOST
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_POOL_LEAVE_LOST

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_STRIP
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_STRIP

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_LEAVE_STANDARD
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_LEAVE_STANDARD

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_POOL
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_POOL

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_PUB_VLAD_ALIVE
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_PUB_VLAD_ALIVE

FCR21AU.original: ~z~You are taking me to Perestroika. I hope that Mr. Faustin gives you an employee discount?
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~你带我来Perestroika啊。Faustin先生会不会给你员工特价？

FCR21AU.original: ~z~You see that girl who was eyeing me, I would have sealed that deal if I didn't have to see Mallorie later.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~看见那个偷瞄我的妹子了吗？要不是跟Mallorie有约会，我就去泡她了。

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVEF_LATE_CAR
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVEF_LATE_CAR

FCR21AU.original: ~z~It is a shame that Mr. Faustin your Russian gangster friend, is dead. The place is going to pot.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~可惜你的俄国黑帮朋友Faustin先生已经死了。这地方也要衰败了。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Niko, you said you'd be here earlier. No matter, you will drive us. If you like you can use a cab.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~Niko，说好了你来这儿等我的。算了，你来开车。需要的话可以开我的车。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Niko, I could suck a Bleeder Burger dry. This is my favorite.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~Niko，我能把一整个吸血鬼堡吸干。这是我的最爱。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Niko, good game. You are good at bowling and I'm good with the ladies. We both have skills.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~Niko，打得不错。你很擅长保龄球，我很擅长对付女人，都有一技之长。

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_LEAVE_PUB_VLAD_DEAD
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_LEAVE_PUB_VLAD_DEAD

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_SHOW_CABARET
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_SHOW_CABARET

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Bowling, Niko. This is a surprise. You know that I like to beat you though. Let's do it.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~保龄球，Niko。这倒是个惊喜，你也知道我喜欢打败你。来吧。

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_DARTS_LEAVE_DRAW
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_DARTS_LEAVE_DRAW

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVEH_NOTLATE
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVEH_NOTLATE

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVEM_NOTLATE
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVEM_NOTLATE

FCR21AU.original: ~z~NB, you are making an important business owner wait for you. I am generous though. You can drive me in one of my cabs.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~NB，你居然让大老板等你，不过我原谅你。你可以开我的出租车。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Niko, you like it when I hold you on these motorbikes, don't you. Let's go.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~Niko，你很喜欢我在摩托上抱着你，对吧。走。

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_LEAVE_CLUB_GENERIC
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_LEAVE_CLUB_GENERIC

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_DARTS_LEAVE_WON
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_DARTS_LEAVE_WON

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Okay cousin, let's have a meal here.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~好了堂弟，进去吃一顿吧。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Late NB, not acceptable. Make it up by driving me in one of my cabs.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~迟到了，NB，不能这样。开我的出租车将功补过吧。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Okay, alright, what's going on?
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~好了，好了，这是什么情况？

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Titties, titties, titties. Let me at them, cousin. Unleash me.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~奶子，奶子，奶子。让我上，堂弟。别拦我。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Thank you, cousin. We should hang out again soon.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~谢谢你，堂弟。过段时间我们再出去一次吧。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Niko, I love that place. Is hard to believe but man cannot live on titties alone.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~Niko，我爱这地方。不过男人居然不能只靠奶子生存。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Ummm, you didn't check this by me. I'm not in the mood, Niko.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~唔，别想让我进去。我没心情，Niko。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~There is a fire in my belly, I like the drinks at that place.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~肚子里的酒正在燃烧，我喜欢那家店的酒水。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~We must settle this some other way. Maybe we should compete over a woman. Clearly not Mallorie though.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~我们想法子决出胜负吧。比如说比赛泡妞，不过我不会用Mallorie比的。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Even without a warmup you will be no match for me on the pool table.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~就算不热身，你在球桌上也不是我的对手。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Ahh, NB. Seeing you puts a smile on my face. Let's go.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~啊，NB，见着你我就笑开了花。走吧。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~哈哈哈哈哈。

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_LEAVE_CLUB_FAUSTIN_DEAD
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_LEAVE_CLUB_FAUSTIN_DEAD

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Oh really, umm, yes.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~其实，呃，是的。

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_SHOW_LATE
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_SHOW_LATE

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Niko. Were you afraid of playing out the game for fear that I would beat you? Do not be scared of defeat, cousin.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~Niko，你是不是怕被我击败才中途退出的？别害怕失败，堂弟。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Thank you in advance for driving me home. Let's go now.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~先说好，谢谢你送我回家。我们走吧。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Ahh, is this where we eat, cousin? Let's do it.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~啊，在这儿吃饭是吧，堂弟？进去吧。

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_CLUB_GENERIC
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_CLUB_GENERIC

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Niko, you are good with a pool cue. You can teach me about that while I teach you about women.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~Niko，你拿上台球杆还挺行的嘛。我教你泡女人，你教我打台球吧。

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_CLUB_FAUSTIN_ALIVE
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_CLUB_FAUSTIN_ALIVE

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Cousin Niko, what's up? We can take one of the cabs. Shotgun not driving.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~Niko堂弟，怎么了？开我的出租也行。我不开车。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Niko, congratulations. It is not often that someone beats me at darts.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~Niko，恭喜啊。很少有人能在飞镖上打败我。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Do you see... do you see something in my eye. I am not seeing so good. Must be how you beat me.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~你看见...看见我眼睛里的东西了吗？我看得不太清楚，这才被你捡漏了。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Oh cousin, I salivate at the thought of all the naked flesh in there. Let's go.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~噢，堂弟，光是想到里面赤裸的肉体我就垂涎欲滴了。

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_CLUB_FAUSTIN_DEAD
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_CLUB_FAUSTIN_DEAD

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_POOL_LEAVE_DRAW
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_POOL_LEAVE_DRAW

FCR21AU.original: ~z~You must be in a hurry, Niko. It does not take long to finish a game of darts with your cousin.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~你是有急事吧，Niko。陪堂兄投完一局飞镖又花不了多久。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~You mind driving your tired cousin home? Thank you.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~介意送你疲倦的堂兄回家吗？谢谢你。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Hey, NB. We can take one of the cabs if you like. You mind driving?
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~嘿，NB。需要的话我可以把出租车借你开。你来开车吧？

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_DARTS_LEAVE_ABANDON
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_DARTS_LEAVE_ABANDON

FCR21AU.original: ~z~That was fun NB. Hit me up if you want to hang out again soon.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~玩得很开心，NB。你要是还想出来玩就打给我。

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_DURING_SHOW_NEG
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_DURING_SHOW_NEG

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Niko, we are evenly matched. There can clearly be no winner when two cousins such as us compete.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~Niko，我们打平了。果然我们兄弟二人是分不出胜负的。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Niko, this is just the place. I hear it is filled with girls with low self esteem.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~Niko，我就想来这里。听说这里有很多不知廉耻的女孩。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~I'll catch you round, NB. Call me if you want to hang out again.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~我们之后见，NB。还想出来玩就联系我。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~I am pissing myself, literally.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~我笑尿了，真的。

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_LEAVE_CLUB_FAUSTIN_ALIVE
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_LEAVE_CLUB_FAUSTIN_ALIVE

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVEC_NOTLATE
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVEC_NOTLATE

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Sorry, Niko. I don't feel like doing this just now.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~抱歉，Niko。我现在不太想来这里。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~I am feeling a little drunk. I don't think they water the drinks down too much at that shit hole.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~我有一点醉了。我看这家店掺水掺得不多。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Let us go now, cousin. Take me home.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~我们该走了，堂弟。送我回家。

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_BOWL_LEAVE_LOST
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_BOWL_LEAVE_LOST

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_PUB_VLAD_DEAD
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_PUB_VLAD_DEAD

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Late, NB. Tut, tut, tut. Let's go.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~迟到了，NB。啧啧啧。走吧。

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_DARTS
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_DARTS

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_DIFF_POOL_YES
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_DIFF_POOL_YES

FCR21AU.original: ~z~We can get a quick bite here, cousin. Let's go.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~我们可以在这儿吃顿快餐，堂弟。走吧。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~NB, my cousin. Why don't we find a car so we can go.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~NB，好堂弟。先找辆车再出发吧。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Fucking Vlad. I cannot help but think of that scumbag in that place.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~狗逼Vlad。我在这儿不由自主地就会想到那个小人。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~We shall drink and remember the old days. I'll buy the first round. That's if I remembered my wallet.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~我们该喝几杯，回忆下过去。前两杯我请。如果我还找得到钱包的话。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~There are better things to do on a pool table than play pool. I could show you the things I'd do to a bored housewife on one.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~台球桌上比起打台球还有更好的事情能做。我可以让你见识下我会对寂寞人妻做的事情。

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_LEAVE_SHOW_EARLY
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_LEAVE_SHOW_EARLY

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_POOL_LEAVE_ABANDON
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_POOL_LEAVE_ABANDON

FCR21AU.original: ~z~There is only one thing I'm better at than playing pool, Niko. And, as a man, you won't get to see me in action.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~我只有一件事是比打台球更擅长的，Niko。但是身为男人，你是无福亲眼见到了。

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_TAKEHOME
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_TAKEHOME

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Call me cousin, I'll see you soon.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~有空找我，堂弟，回头见。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Okay, I am ready to go home. You will drive your cousin.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~好了，我准备好回家了。由你送堂兄回家。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Ahh, Comrades. We shall raise our glasses to the late Vlad while we're here.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~啊，Comrades酒吧。在店里的时候得敬Vlad一杯。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~It is a shame we did not meet Vlad in there. I wanted to tell him what a good loanshark he is.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~没在这儿见到Vlad真是可惜。我还想告诉他他这个放贷的有多好呢。

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_LEAVE_FASTFOOD
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_LEAVE_FASTFOOD

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Later, Niko. Give me a call sometime, okay?
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~回见，Niko。有空给我打电话，好吧？

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Niko, you're pretty good. It's clearly those Bellic genes you've got. If we were a team we'd be unstoppable.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~Niko，你真棒，完全表现了你的Bellic家基因。我们组队就无人能敌了。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~This is so funny, cousin. Don't you think? Don't you think?
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~太好笑了啊，堂弟。不是吗？不是吗？

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_LEAVE_BURGER_SHOT
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_LEAVE_BURGER_SHOT

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Niko, you rack 'em up and I'll knock 'em in. Let's go.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~Niko，把球安排好，我一个个打进去。开始吧。

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVEF_NOTLATE
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVEF_NOTLATE

FCR21AU.original: ~z~What a nice place this is. If I didn't know better I would have thought you were trying to fuck me.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~这家店好啊。要不是我更懂行，我就要以为你是想睡我了。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Niko, I was starting to think you wouldn't come. Let's go now.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~Niko，我还以为你不来了呢。我们走吧。

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_LEAVE_HIGHEND
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_LEAVE_HIGHEND

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Do not worry about losing. At least you are better at stealing cars and shooting things.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~输了也别担心。至少你偷车打枪比我强。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Okay Niko, watch out for all the bullseyes I will be getting.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~好了，Niko。等着看我把靶心扎烂吧。

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_DARTS_LEAVE_LOST
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_DARTS_LEAVE_LOST

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_LEAVE_PUB_VLAD_ALIVE
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_LEAVE_PUB_VLAD_ALIVE

FCR21AU.original: ~z~You see, aren't you pleased you are not in Old Country where that is all that is on.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~你看，只要不是在故国演出，你不就能看得很开心了吗。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~What have you been doing, cousin? We missed the damn show.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~你他妈在干嘛，堂弟？演出早就开始了。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Next time let us finish the game, okay?
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~下次我们打完整局吧，好吗？

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Is time to go back home, will you take me?
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~现在该回家了，能送我回去吗？

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_SHOW_COMEDY
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_SHOW_COMEDY

FCR21AU.original: ~z~I am no longer hungry, cousin. That was good.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~我现在不饿了，堂弟。真不错。

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_DURING_SHOW_POS
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_DURING_SHOW_POS

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Niko, you are really moving up in the world, no? I tell you we are going to the top when you arrive.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~Niko，你这越来越高端了啊。你刚来的时候我就说过我们会走上顶峰。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Oh cousin, I wish I could get angry at you for being late but you're too loveable. Let's go.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~噢，堂弟，你实在是太可爱了，就算迟到我也生不了你的气。我们走吧。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Mallorie would love this, I tell you she would.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~Mallorie也会喜欢的，我知道的。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Niko. You had lost before we even got here. Darts is about having the mental edge
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~Niko，来美国前你也老输给我。飞镖需要的是心理优势。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Cousin, you are late. For that you are driving. I will let you use a cab if you want to though.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~堂弟，你迟到了，所以你来开车。需要的话我可以把出租车借给你。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Niko, how could you expect to beat someone as supremely skilled as me? It was foolish
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~Niko，你怎么可能打赢我这样球技精湛的人呢？太蠢了。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~I wait and I wait and now you come without even a car. Well, let us find one.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~我等啊等等啊等，结果现在你连辆车都没有就来了。算了，找辆车吧。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~See you later, NB. Give me a call, yes?
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~回头见，NB。记得联系我，行吧？

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Take me back won't you?
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~送我回去吧，好吗？

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Maybe we will play a whole game the next time we bowl, cousin.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~下次打保龄球的时候把整局打完吧，堂弟。

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_POOL_LEAVE_WON
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_POOL_LEAVE_WON

FCR21AU.original: ~z~That served it's purpose cousin, my stomach is full.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~目标达成了，堂弟，我吃饱了。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~You're late but I can't stay mad at you. Let's go.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~你迟到了，但我没法对你生气。我们走吧。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Do you get it cousin, do you get it?
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~听懂了吗，堂弟？听懂了吗？

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Niko, there you are. Why don't you drive me in one of the cabs?
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~Niko，你来啦。你可以开我店里的出租车。

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_DIFF_ACTIVITY_NO
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_DIFF_ACTIVITY_NO

FCR21AU.original: ~z~What amazing burgers, I feel another chin growing on my face. Do you see it?
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~汉堡太棒了，觉得自己又长了一层下巴。你看见了吗？

FCR21AU.original: ~z~I like that place, now that Vlad is gone I can really appreciate the atmosphere.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~我喜欢这家酒吧，现在Vlad不在了，我才能真正享受店里的氛围。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~I could have beaten you with my eyes closed, cousin. I'm sorry but I'm that much better.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~我闭着眼睛都能打败你，堂弟。不好意思，我就是比你强。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~I didn't sign up for this, cousin. What gives?
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~跟说好的不一样啊，堂弟。怎么回事？

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Niko, why you want to leave, cousin? We could have at least seen the end.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~Niko，你为什么想走了，堂弟？我们至少可以看完的。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~I enjoyed that, Niko. We should do it again soon.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~我玩得很高兴，Niko。我们过几天再出来吧。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Niko, we have left now but those titties will inhabit my dreams for many nights to come.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~Niko，虽然我们出来了，但那些奶子会在我的梦里住很多晚上的。

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_STANDARD
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_STANDARD

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Niko, you call yourself a criminal but the real crime would be coming home without a lady tonight. Let's go.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~Niko，你自称是罪犯，但今晚不带个女人回家才是罪过。走吧。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~I worry for you, cousin. How could any red blooded male want to leave all those lovely titties so soon?
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~我很替你担心啊，堂弟。血气方刚的男人怎么会这么快就离开那些可爱的奶子呢？

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Niko, you are treating your cousin right. This is very sweet of you.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~Niko，你对堂兄我真好。我很感谢。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Take me home, Niko.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~送我回家，Niko。

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_PUB_GENERIC
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_PUB_GENERIC

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Ladies watch out, the cousins Bellic are here. You are not safe.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~女士们当心，Bellic兄弟来也。你们危险了。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~I'm not really feeling the vibe right now, cousin.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~我现在真没那个兴趣，堂弟。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Those Russians are sure a strange group, no?
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~那群俄国人是个奇怪的组织，不是吗？

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Cousin, let us go.You can drive me in one of my cabs if you like.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~堂弟，出发吧。需要的话我这些出租随你开。

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_FASTFOOD
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_FASTFOOD

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Ok we can fill up with good American food. I'm in the mood for a hormone and chemical hit
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~好了，可以享用美味的美国食物了。我现在就想来一顿激素和添加剂套餐。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Niko, you lazy bastard. All your screwing around has made us miss the show.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~Niko，你个懒鬼。到处乱转转得我们错过演出了。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~I am not so sure about this one.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~这一出我不好说。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Niko, why you so impatient? We could have stayed until the end.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~Niko，你怎么这么急？我们可以待到表演结束的。

FCR21AU.original: ~z~Can you drop me off at home, cousin?
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~你能送我回家吗，堂弟？

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_DIFF_BOWL_YES
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_DIFF_BOWL_YES

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_LEAVE_PUB_GENERIC
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_LEAVE_PUB_GENERIC

FCR21AU.original: ~z~You must have happy memories of your time here with the late Mr. Faustin. Isn't that right, cousin?
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~你在这儿肯定有和Faustin先生一起的美好回忆，对不对，堂弟？

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_BOWL_LEAVE_ABANDON
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_BOWL_LEAVE_ABANDON

FCR21AU.original: ~z~You keep your cousin waiting, is a disgrace NB. Now, we must find a car.
FCR21AU.translated: ~z~让你堂兄一直等着，太可耻了，NB。现在先找辆车吧。

FCR21AU.original: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_BURGER_SHOT
FCR21AU.translated: FCR2_ACT_ARRIVE_BURGER_SHOT
